  "detailed_description": "Unleash bolts, set traps, and bash through relentless hordes of creatures to protect a little girl from Hera's wrath in this rogue-lite shooter. Astraea is a heart-pounding experience where you must prevent anything on the ground from reaching the girl while dealing with your own threats in the air.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2> <br><strong>Engaging Story</strong><br><br>Immerse yourself in a fully-voiced and captivating story that unfolds in and out of battle. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fast Progression</strong><br><br>Choose from Zeus' blessings to improve everything from your accuracy to your curse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>More Challenges</strong><br><br>Test your skills with unlockable difficulties, and complete numerous challenges and feats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Hidden Collectables</strong><br><br>Find hidden collectables while fending off the relentless waves of Hera’s minions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Endless Mode</strong><br><br>Face off against an endless horde of minions in Endless Mode.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d2508f381035c8f49792c03d44117549.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=552 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d2508f381035c8f49792c03d44117549.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d2508f381035c8f49792c03d44117549.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Unleash bolts, set traps, and bash through relentless hordes of creatures to protect a little girl from Hera's wrath in this rogue-lite shooter. Astraea is a heart-pounding experience where you must prevent anything on the ground from reaching the girl while dealing with your own threats in the air.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2> <br><strong>Engaging Story</strong><br><br>Immerse yourself in a fully-voiced and captivating story that unfolds in and out of battle. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fast Progression</strong><br><br>Choose from Zeus' blessings to improve everything from your accuracy to your curse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>More Challenges</strong><br><br>Test your skills with unlockable difficulties, and complete numerous challenges and feats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Hidden Collectables</strong><br><br>Find hidden collectables while fending off the relentless waves of Hera’s minions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Endless Mode</strong><br><br>Face off against an endless horde of minions in Endless Mode.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d2508f381035c8f49792c03d44117549.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=552 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d2508f381035c8f49792c03d44117549.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta